com.percussion.services.catalog
Enum PSTypeEnum

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<PSTypeEnum>
      com.percussion.services.catalog.PSTypeEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<PSTypeEnum>
public enum PSTypeEnum
extends Enum<PSTypeEnum>

This enum lists all types in the system that participate in cataloging. The ordinal value of these values is used when creating guids. Ordinal values must be unique.

Author:
dougrand
